[
    {
        "text": "There are deserts all over the world.",
        "startTime": 2700,
        "endTime": 4900,
        "slowStartTime": 4250,
        "slowEndTime": 7550
    },
    {
        "text": "They can be found in Africa, China, South America and North America.",
        "startTime": 5250,
        "endTime": 9300,
        "slowStartTime": 8100,
        "slowEndTime": 14200
    },
    {
        "text": "In some places, deserts are growing.",
        "startTime": 9750,
        "endTime": 12000,
        "slowStartTime": 14800,
        "slowEndTime": 18200
    },
    {
        "text": "This is a serious problem because deserts destroy farmland,...",
        "startTime": 12400,
        "endTime": 16400,
        "slowStartTime": 18800,
        "slowEndTime": 24900
    },
    {
        "text": "...and ruin land where animals live.",
        "startTime": 16650,
        "endTime": 18700,
        "slowStartTime": 25200,
        "slowEndTime": 28300
    },
    {
        "text": "When people cannot grow food or find animals to eat,...",
        "startTime": 19350,
        "endTime": 22450,
        "slowStartTime": 29200,
        "slowEndTime": 33900
    },
    {
        "text": "...they have to leave their homes.",
        "startTime": 22750,
        "endTime": 24050,
        "slowStartTime": 34300,
        "slowEndTime": 36300
    },
    {
        "text": "Sometimes, nature can cause deserts to spread.",
        "startTime": 24450,
        "endTime": 27250,
        "slowStartTime": 36850,
        "slowEndTime": 41050
    },
    {
        "text": "Wind can move sand away from deserts and onto useful land.",
        "startTime": 27750,
        "endTime": 31550,
        "slowStartTime": 41800,
        "slowEndTime": 47600
    },
    {
        "text": "When there is no rain for a long time, plants die and deserts grow.",
        "startTime": 32050,
        "endTime": 36450,
        "slowStartTime": 48250,
        "slowEndTime": 54900
    },
    {
        "text": "However, humans can also cause deserts to grow.",
        "startTime": 36900,
        "endTime": 40100,
        "slowStartTime": 55520,
        "slowEndTime": 60400
    },
    {
        "text": "This is called desertification and it happens in many ways.",
        "startTime": 40550,
        "endTime": 44350,
        "slowStartTime": 61050,
        "slowEndTime": 66800
    },
    {
        "text": "One way is when people cause too much air pollution,...",
        "startTime": 44900,
        "endTime": 48100,
        "slowStartTime": 67500,
        "slowEndTime": 72400
    },
    {
        "text": "...which can make an area hotter.",
        "startTime": 48250,
        "endTime": 49750,
        "slowStartTime": 72550,
        "slowEndTime": 74850
    },
    {
        "text": "Hotter weather can reduce the amount of rain as well.",
        "startTime": 50550,
        "endTime": 53050,
        "slowStartTime": 76000,
        "slowEndTime": 79800
    },
    {
        "text": "Too many people in one area can also damage the land.",
        "startTime": 53650,
        "endTime": 56650,
        "slowStartTime": 80700,
        "slowEndTime": 85200
    },
    {
        "text": "In addition, having many animals can harm the land.",
        "startTime": 57400,
        "endTime": 60350,
        "slowStartTime": 86300,
        "slowEndTime": 90700
    },
    {
        "text": "When large animals like cows walk on soil too much, they turn it into dust.",
        "startTime": 60800,
        "endTime": 65800,
        "slowStartTime": 91400,
        "slowEndTime": 98900
    },
    {
        "text": "The wind easily blows this dust away.",
        "startTime": 66400,
        "endTime": 68700,
        "slowStartTime": 99750,
        "slowEndTime": 103300
    },
    {
        "text": "Trees help hold water in the ground.",
        "startTime": 69450,
        "endTime": 71700,
        "slowStartTime": 104350,
        "slowEndTime": 107800
    },
    {
        "text": "When people cut down too many trees,...",
        "startTime": 72300,
        "endTime": 74400,
        "slowStartTime": 108600,
        "slowEndTime": 111800
    },
    {
        "text": "...less water stays in the ground and the soil is ruined.",
        "startTime": 74700,
        "endTime": 77700,
        "slowStartTime": 112250,
        "slowEndTime": 116750
    },
    {
        "text": "All of these things can speed up desertification.",
        "startTime": 78700,
        "endTime": 81700,
        "slowStartTime": 118200,
        "slowEndTime": 122800
    },
    {
        "text": "To stop deserts from growing, people must think of ways to treat the land better.",
        "startTime": 82400,
        "endTime": 86750,
        "slowStartTime": 123800,
        "slowEndTime": 130400
    }
]